Super Block is a browser extension that blocks ads from showing up on websites you visit.

There are many reasons to use Super Block, including:

ğŸ›‘ Powerful Adblocking - Remove advertisements from websites, giving you a cleaner and more enjoyable browsing experience.

ğŸ”’ Enhance Privacy - Stop trackers from collecting data about your online activities, keeping your browsing habits more private.

ğŸ›¡ï¸ Improve Security - Protect against malicious ads and websites that could harm your device or steal personal information.

ğŸ‘Œ Easy to Use - Designed for simplicity, it works right out of the box with no setup required.

âš¡ Faster Loading Speeds - Pages load quicker without the extra data from ads, so you can browse more efficiently.

ğŸ”‹ Longer Battery Life - Consumes less battery by blocking energy-draining ads.

ğŸª¶ Lightweight - Designed to be resource-efficient so it doesnâ€™t slow down your browser.

ğŸ“„ Whitelist - Support your favorite sites by allowing ads on them through a simple whitelist feature.

There are many reasons to use Super Block, including:

âš¡ Faster Loading Speeds - Pages load quicker without the extra data from ads, so you can browse more efficiently.
